---
description: Solidus is the free, open-source eCommerce platform based on Ruby on Rails for digitally-native brands, fast-growing online businesses and pragmatic developers.
---

<div class="dark-background">
  <div class="homepage-hero hero-block content-block--skewed content-block-white">
    <div class="content-wrapper container">
      <div class="row align-items-center">
        <div class="col-lg">
          <div class="pr-lg-6 mb-3">
            <h1 class="title">The only eCommerce platform youâ€™ll ever need.</h1>
            <p class="lead mb-6">
              Build, customize and scale your store with no limits or license fees. Solidus is the
              free, open-source eCommerce framework for digitally-native brands, fast-growing online
              businesses and pragmatic developers.
            </p>
            <a class="btn btn-primary btn-lg" href="/get-started">Get started</a>
            <a class="btn btn-secondary btn-white" href="http://demo.solidus.io/" target="_blank">Demo</a>
            <div class="mt-4 mb-4">
              <%= inline_svg("icons/check-circle-green.svg", class: "isvg") %>
              <span class="pr-sm-4 pr-2">
                <small>100% free</small>
              </span>
              <%= inline_svg("icons/check-circle-green.svg", class: "isvg") %>
              <span>
                <small>Open-source</small>
              </span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-lg">
          <div class="hero-image-wrapper">
            <%= inline_svg("illustrations/solidus-hero-home.svg", class: "hero-image") %>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="intro content-block--skewed content-block-gray-100">
    <div class="content-wrapper pt-0 pb-0">
      <div class="content-block pt-0">
        <div class="container-fluid">
          <p class="lead text-gray-600 text-center font-weight-light mb-md-8 mb-5">
            Solidus powers the brands defining the future of eCommerce.
          </p>
          <%= partial "partials/community_logos" %>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="container container-md text-center">
        <h2 class="title">Yours to customize, yours forever.</h2>
        <p class="lead">
          Free your business from useless limitations. Solidus gives you the freedom to change and
          iterate as much as you want. Start small, grow big: discover what moves the needle for
          your brand and make it happen.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="features-section first container">
        <div class="content-block">
          <div class="row align-items-center">
            <div class="features-section--image tab-content col-md">
              <div class="tab-pane active fade show pr-lg-6" id="truly-flexible" role="tabpanel">
                <div class="center-image">
                  <img src="<%= image_path('illustrations/truly-flexible@2x.png') %>" data-srcset="<%= image_path('illustrations/truly-flexible@2x.png') %> 2x, <%= image_path('illustrations/truly-flexible@1x.png') %> 1x" class="img-fluid" alt="Truly Flexible" width="100%" >
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="tab-pane fade pr-lg-6" id="endlessly-scalable" role="tabpanel">
                <div class="center-image">
                  <img src="<%= image_path('illustrations/endlessly-scalable.svg') %>" data-src="<%= image_path('illustrations/endlessly-scalable.svg') %>" class="img-fluid" alt="Endlessly Scalable" width="100%" >
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="tab-pane fade pr-lg-6" id="stable-reliable" role="tabpanel">
                <div class="center-image">
                  <img src="<%= image_path('illustrations/stable-and-reliable@2x.png') %>" data-srcset="<%= image_path('illustrations/stable-and-reliable@2x.png') %> 2x, <%= image_path('illustrations/stable-and-reliable@1x.png') %> 1x" class="img-fluid" alt="Stable and Reliable" width="100%" >
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="features-section--paragraph col-md">
              <ul class="nav tab-hover pl-lg-6" data-mouse="hover">
                <li class="nav-item">
                  <div class="img-wrap mb-0">
                    <img src="<%= image_path('illustrations/truly-flexible@2x.png') %>" data-srcset="<%= image_path('illustrations/truly-flexible@2x.png') %> 2x, <%= image_path('illustrations/truly-flexible@1x.png') %> 1x" class="img-fluid" alt="Truly Flexible" width="100%" >
                  </div>
                  <a class="nav-link active" data-toggle="tab" role="tab" href="#truly-flexible">
                    <h4>Truly flexible</h4>
                    <p>
                      Solidus adapts to your business, not the other way around. Integrate anything
                      and customize everything, without technical limitations.
                    </p>
                  </a>
                </li>
                <li class="nav-item">
                  <div class="img-wrap">
                    <img src="<%= image_path('illustrations/endlessly-scalable.svg') %>" data-src="<%= image_path('illustrations/endlessly-scalable.svg') %>" class="img-fluid" alt="Endlessly Scalable" width="100%" >
                  </div>
                  <a class="nav-link" data-toggle="tab" role="tab" href="#endlessly-scalable">
                    <h4>Built to scale</h4>
                    <p>
                      Adapt and react to any scenario. Solidus handles the complexity and removes
                      the headache of scaling from small to enterprise.
                    </p>
                  </a>
                </li>
                <li class="nav-item">
                  <div class="img-wrap">
                    <img src="<%= image_path('illustrations/stable-and-reliable@2x.png') %>" data-srcset="<%= image_path('illustrations/stable-and-reliable@2x.png') %> 2x, <%= image_path('illustrations/stable-and-reliable@1x.png') %> 1x" class="img-fluid" alt="Stable and Reliable" width="100%">
                  </div>
                  <a class="nav-link" data-toggle="tab" role="tab" href="#stable-reliable">
                    <h4>Stable and reliable</h4>
                    <p>
                      Built upon the shared knowledge of the brands that revolutionized eCommerce,
                      Solidus is a production-grade, battle-tested tool for serious ventures.
                    </p>
                  </a>
                </li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="features-section second container">
        <div class="content-block p-0">
          <div class="row align-items-center">
            <div class="features-section--image tab-content col-md order-md-2">
              <div class="tab-pane active fade show pl-lg-6" id="free-forever" role="tabpanel">
                <div class="center-image">
                  <img src="<%= image_path('illustrations/free-forever@2x.png') %>" data-srcset="<%= image_path('illustrations/free-forever@2x.png') %> 2x, <%= image_path('illustrations/free-forever@1x.png') %> 1x" class="img-fluid" alt="Free Forever" width="100%" >
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="tab-pane fade pl-lg-6 text-center" id="secure-by-default" role="tabpanel">
                <div class="center-image">
                  <img src="<%= image_path('illustrations/secure-by-default.svg') %>" data-src="<%= image_path('illustrations/secure-by-default.svg') %>" class="img-fluid" alt="Secure by Default" width="350">
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="tab-pane fade pl-lg-6 text-center" id="easy-adoption" role="tabpanel">
                <div class="center-image">
                  <img src="<%= image_path('illustrations/easy-adoption@2x.png') %>" data-srcset="<%= image_path('illustrations/easy-adoption@2x.png') %> 2x, <%= image_path('illustrations/easy-adoption@1x.png') %> 1x" class="img-fluid" alt="Easy Adoption" width="400">
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="features-section--paragraph left-block col-md order-md-1">
              <ul class="nav tab-hover pr-lg-6" data-mouse="hover">
                <li class="nav-item">
                  <div class="img-wrap">
                    <img src="<%= image_path('illustrations/free-forever@2x.png') %>" data-srcset="<%= image_path('illustrations/free-forever@2x.png') %> 2x, <%= image_path('illustrations/free-forever@1x.png') %> 1x" class="img-fluid" alt="Free Forever" width="100%" >
                  </div>
                  <a class="nav-link active" data-toggle="tab" role="tab" href="#free-forever">
                    <h4>Free for everyone</h4>
                    <p>
                      Forget about revenue-share models, license fees and expensive plugins. Invest
                      in what matters the most: your brand, your technology.
                    </p>
                  </a>
                </li>
                <li class="nav-item">
                  <div class="img-wrap pl-3 pr-3 pl-md-0 pr-md-0">
                    <img src="<%= image_path('illustrations/secure-by-default.svg') %>" data-src="<%= image_path('illustrations/secure-by-default.svg') %>" class="img-fluid" alt="Secure by Default" width="350">
                  </div>
                  <a class="nav-link" data-toggle="tab" role="tab" href="#secure-by-default">
                    <h4>Secure by default</h4>
                    <p>
                      Sleep tight knowing your store is safe. We got your back with automated
                      security fixes, a clear disclosure policy and strict code reviews.
                    </p>
                  </a>
                </li>
                <li class="nav-item">
                  <div class="img-wrap pl-3 pr-3 pl-md-0 pr-md-0">
                    <img src="<%= image_path('illustrations/easy-adoption@2x.png') %>" data-srcset="<%= image_path('illustrations/easy-adoption@2x.png') %> 2x, <%= image_path('illustrations/easy-adoption@1x.png') %> 1x" class="img-fluid" alt="Easy Adoption" width="400">
                  </div>
                  <a class="nav-link" data-toggle="tab" role="tab" href="#easy-adoption">
                    <h4>Community-centric</h4>
                    <p>
                      Community edition is the only edition. Build your brand on top of a truly
                      open-source, community-driven platform that multiplies your competitive
                      advantage.
                    </p>
                  </a>
                </li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="open-source-section">
    <div class="testimonials content-block pb-0">
      <div class="container text-center">
        <%= partial "partials/testimonials_list" %>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="container">
      <div class="content-block">
        <div class="row align-items-center content-block-gray-900">
          <div class="col-md-5 col-lg-6 col-xl-7"  data-aos="fade">
            <div class="pr-md-6">
              <%= partial 'partials/community_stats', locals: { type: 'github', count: data.project_stats.github_stars, title: 'GitHub stars' } %>
              <%= partial 'partials/community_stats', locals: { type: 'slack', count: data.project_stats.slack_members, title: 'Slack members' } %>
              <%= partial 'partials/community_stats', locals: { type: 'open-collective', count_prefix: '$', count: data.project_stats.open_collective_donations, count_k: 'K', title: 'Donated' } %>
              <%= partial 'partials/community_stats', locals: { type: 'contributors', count: data.project_stats.contributors, title: 'Contributors' } %>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-7 col-lg-6 col-xl-5">
            <div class="pl-md-6">
              <h2 class="title mt-4">A truly open-source mindset</h2>
              <div class="mb-4 mt-4">
                <h4>Driven collectively</h4>
                <p>
                  Solidus is created by a dedicated group of passionate developers, agencies and
                  retailers that work together to move the platform forward.
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="mb-4">
                <h4>Funded transparently</h4>
                <p>
                  Our <a href="/contributors"><b>community</b></a> supports Solidus with financial contributions through
                  OpenCollective. The funds are used to improve and promote the platform.
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="mb-4">
                <h4>Developed publicly</h4>
                <p>
                  Our roadmap is defined and executed in public. See what we're working on right now
                  and where we're headed next. Even better, be a part of it.
                </p>
              </div>
              <a class="btn btn-primary" href="/roadmap">Check out our roadmap</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="ruby-on-rails content-block pt-0">
        <div class="row align-items-center content-block-gray-900">
          <div class="col-lg pl-lg-6 order-lg-2">
            <div class="terminal-window mb-8 mb-lg-0" data-aos="fade">
              <div class="terminal-header mb-3">
                <span class="close-btn"></span>
                <span class="minimize-btn ml-1 mr-1"></span>
                <span class="zoom-btn"></span>
              </div>
              <div class="terminal-body">
                <pre>
                  <code class="comment line-0"># Add the Solidus gem to your Rails application</code>
                  <code class="line line-1">gem '<span class="highlighted">solidus</span>'<span class="cursor-1">_</span></code>
                  <code class="comment mt-2 line-3"># Install dependencies</code>
                  <code class="line line-4">$ bundle<span class="cursor-4">_</span></code>
                  <code class="comment mt-2 line-5"># Install Solidus</code>
                  <code class="line line-6">$ bin/rails g solidus:install<span class="cursor-6">_</span></code>
                  <code class="comment mt-2 line-10"># Start the server</code>
                  <code class="line line-11">$ bundle <span class="highlighted">exec</span> rails s<span class="cursor-11">_</span></code>
                  <code class="comment mt-2 line-12"># Visit the local server</code>
                  <code class="line line-13">http://localhost:3000/<span class="cursor-13">_</span></code>
                </pre>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col-lg pr-lg-6 order-lg-1">
            <h2 class="title">Powered by <span class="text-danger">Ruby on Rails</span>.</h2>
            <p class="mb-4">
              Solidus is powered by Ruby on Rails, the framework used by the most popular online
              companies such as <b>Basecamp, GitHub, Shopify, Airbnb, Twitch, SoundCloud, Hulu,
              Zendesk and Square</b>.
            </p>
            <a class="btn btn-primary mb-4" href="https://guides.solidus.io/">Read our Guides</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row pt-8 content-block-gray-900">
          <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
            <h4 class="title">Fast iteration</h4>
            <p>
              Solidus is excellent for building MVPs and iterating quickly. It doesn't matter if you
              only have one developer or an agile team of 50, Solidus has the flexibility to drive
              your store.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
            <h4 class="title">Future-proof stack</h4>
            <p>
              When it comes to your business, you shouldn't have to choose between modern and
              stable. Ruby and Ruby on Rails are mature, powerful technologies that are here to
              stay.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-4">
            <h4 class="title">Large ecosystem</h4>
            <p>
              Ruby on Rails boasts one of the largest and highest-quality development ecosystems,
              which makes it easy to find help and build a world-class team for your brand.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <%= partial "partials/cta_bottom" %>
</div>
